- cs.MS (Mathematical Software): The paper discusses the challenges of maintaining a user-friendly high-level interface while generating efficient, vectorized code for the finite element method, which is a topic within mathematical software. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses code transformation and optimization techniques for achieving efficient vectorization, which are topics within software engineering. 
- cs.CE (Computer Engineering): The paper evaluates the performance of the vectorized code on two recent CPUs, which is a topic within computer engineering. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses code transformation techniques for generating efficient, vectorized code, which is a topic within programming languages.
